Goldman, Honeywell Invest in Aldermore Bank, Telegraph Says

-- B y   C a t h e r i n e   A i r l i e
-- 
2011-09-25T06:32:51Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-25/goldman-honeywell-invest-in-aldermore-bank-telegraph-says.html
A unit of  Goldman Sachs Group Inc. (GS) 
has invested in Aldermore Bank Plc, a specialist in business
loans, the Sunday Telegraph reported, without saying where it
got the information.  Honeywell Capital Management LLC and the Ohio Public
Employees Retirement System have also invested in Aldermore, as
part of 62 million pounds ($96 million) in total funding for the
Peterborough, England-based bank, according to the report.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Catherine Airlie in London at 
 cairlie@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Stephen Voss at 
 sev@bloomberg.net  